high_descs: turn around and walk forwards to the center of the bathroom sink counter
pick up a bar of soap off of the bathroom sink counter
move to the left a bit to face the bathroom sink on the left
place the bar of soap inside of the sink and rinse it off, then pick it back up
turn around and walk to the end of the room, then hang a right turn and walk over to the garbage bin on the floor at the end of the room
place the bar of soap inside of the garbage bin
anns.task_desc: place a rinsed off bar of soap inside of the garbage bin

high_descs: Pick up the bar soap in between the sinks.
Take a step to the left to face the left sink
Place the bar soap in it, wash the soap, and pick it back up.
Turn around, walk towards the door, and then turn right towards the metal bin on the floor.
place the soap in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned soap in the metal bin.

high_descs: Turn around and stand at the counter between the double sinks.
Pick up the bar of soap from the counter top.
Go left and stand in front of the sink on the left.
Put the soap in the sink, turn the water on, turn the water off and take the soap out of the sink.
Turn around and approach the silver waste basket on the floor in the corner.
Put the soap in the waste basket.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap in the waste basket.
